headline: Stocks Set for Muted Open as Investors Await Nvidia Earnings and U.S. Jobs Data
summary: December S&P 500 E-Mini futures (ESZ25) are up +0.02%, and December Nasdaq 100 E-Mini futures (NQZ25) are up +0.09% this morning, pointing to a muted open on Wall Street as cautious sentiment prevailed at the start of a busy week.

headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock to Keep an Eye On and 2 We Find Risky
summary: A company that generates cash isn’t automatically a winner. Some businesses stockpile cash but fail to reinvest wisely, limiting their ability to expand.
